short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Hole In The Wall In A Popup

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Simple Hole In The Wall Game in a popup. Dodge the walls and make your way through the holes. Up and down arrows are the controls. This is a fun game to play no matter where you are, it requires no internet and all you have to do is to click the hole in the wall icon in your extensions.
